race.comment: ATLANTIC DIVA (9) bumped into some handy types in his two race starts and comes here as a leading contender. Sat on the speed when a narrow fifth over 1200m at Canberra. Can get into the right position today and take holding out. DIFRONZO (3) up sharply in distance when a rapid improver to go under narrowly when second over 1400m at Canberra. Can keep the momentum going in this easier race. VALENTIAGO (5) tough ask from the wide gate at his first run back from a lengthy break when eighth over 1300m at Randwick Kensington. Can bounce back quickly today in this weaker contest. INZAIN BABY (6) Hello Youmzain gelding from All Day Baby on debut for the Baker yard. Has shown ability in all four trials and gets his chance today.
